{"tid":2225323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美眾議院共和黨「中國工作組」報告提及香港","createTime":"2020-10-01T08:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T08:41:59.000Z","uid":278587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d05f09ce1fd11ce7afc7eaf211e157aa1e344f7","tid":2225323,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407542&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w11YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=6c9b3fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407542&h=5de5313a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407542</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國眾議院發表兩份報告，全面檢視與中國的關係，建議華府在經濟、情報等多方面作出改革，否則無法與北京競爭。兩份報告都有提及香港。<br />\n<br />\n由美國眾議院共和黨人牽頭成立的「中國工作組」與多位美國官員、企業領袖、專家等會面後，發表130頁報告，形容中國是「世代的威脅」，有如冷戰時期的蘇聯一樣。<br />\n<br />\n報告建議評估是否要全面實施因應中國共產黨鎮壓香港而通過的制裁法例，評估中共對新疆維吾爾族的「罪行」是否構成「種族滅絕」，以及是否要進一步採取行動，回應中共侵犯人權。<br />\n<br />\n報告檢視了六大範疇，包括國家安全、科技、經濟及能源，並作出400項建議，包括把美國重要產業的供應鏈由中國撤出，以免在經濟上完全依賴中國，同時加強部分與中國有關的投資的限制；又建議眾議院跟隨參議院通過法案，把無法符合美國會計準則的中國企業，從證券交易所名單中剔除。<br />\n<br />\n報告又提到是時候修改對台政策，包括與台灣展開貿易協議談判，允許駐美代表處改以「台灣」命名等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由民主黨領導的眾議院情報委員會亦發表報告，指假如不作出改革，改變資源及優先次序的調配，美國情報機關日後將難以與中國競爭。<br />\n<br />\n報告促全面檢視情報蒐集方式，把關注重點從傳統的反恐領域，轉向其他非軍事性的「軟性」安全威脅上，例如公眾衞生、氣候變化等；同時建議重整資源調配，擴大情報機關，培育中國分析人士的項目範圍，並培訓具有中國專業知識的情報官員。<br />\n<br />\n這份報告亦有提及香港，指從香港現況反映出即使在「一國兩制」下，亦不會有真正的民主。"},{"pid":"11ceac2f78384a6cc7ba2cd62a978370af019157","tid":2225323,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276632aa0516fb5eb510aef1b855ca0206d5ff0d","tid":2225323,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a1adc2493f3918f78538b189ef2ce311cd569c","tid":2225323,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900fc9e3a9ab9d67845fe14b2448cfc7e121f7bf","tid":2225323,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d5c4af7e7c6f9fa459504ee03dab09b9a3e403","tid":2225323,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"拜登一上台用老人痴呆做武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即取消所有香港台灣新疆法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理撚得你民主共和兩黨共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜登理撚得你個VP黑婆有支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}